headline: Garmin named one of the Most Innovative Fitness and Wellness Companies of 2025 by Athletech News
summary: Garmin (NYSE: GRMN) has been recognized as one of the Most Innovative Fitness and Wellness Companies of 2025 by Athletech News. The award honors brands worldwide whose products, services and solutions are changing the health, fitness and wellness industry.
